thread.title: Anne

author: Anne
title: Anne
text: My sideboard arrived in perfect shape earlier than expected. The moving company (free shipping) was professional, timely and called before arriving. They brought the piece right into my living room. There was no assembly required (I think I had to put on a couple of handles). The sideboard is lovely. Made very well. Dovetail drawers. Very functional. I really could not be more pleased.
